Ya.

9
00:00:36,077 --> 00:00:37,454
Ya! Macam itulah!

10
00:00:43,168 --> 00:00:44,961
Helo, Lucas.

11
00:00:45,045 --> 00:00:50,175
Ya. Max. Sedarlah, Max. Ini saya.
Saya ada. Saya ada di sini, Max.

12
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:58,767
Awak okey tak?
Ada rasa sakit di mana-mana?

13
00:01:00,101 --> 00:01:04,189
Saya tak rasa apa-apa sangat.

14
00:01:04,939 --> 00:01:07,859
Awak boleh rasa ini?
Awak boleh rasa tangan saya?

15
00:01:08,902 --> 00:01:09,819
Sikit.

16
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:12,530
Awak boleh nampak tak?

17
00:01:13,323 --> 00:01:18,578
Lampu itu betul-betul terang.

18
00:01:19,621 --> 00:01:20,497
Hei.

19
00:01:21,081 --> 00:01:24,876
Awak dah terlalu lama
tak guna mata dan otot awak.

20
00:01:25,919 --> 00:01:27,754
Badan awak cuma lemah,

21
00:01:27,837 --> 00:01:30,840
tapi awak perlu biasakan diri
dan belajar semula.

22
00:01:32,509 --> 00:01:34,094
Awak okey.

23
00:01:35,261 --> 00:01:36,304
Awak okey.

24
00:01:39,349 --> 00:01:40,850
Saya tahu awak ada.

25
00:01:42,477 --> 00:01:44,395
Saya tahu awak masih ada.

26
00:01:46,356 --> 00:01:47,732
Saya nampak awak.

27
00:01:49,109 --> 00:01:50,652
Menunggu saya

28
00:01:50,735 --> 00:01:53,822
sambil mainkan lagu saya.

29
