selama ini…

33
00:02:14,050 --> 00:02:15,802
saya tak perlukannya pun.

34
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,639
Saya hanya perlukan awak.

35
00:02:22,642 --> 00:02:23,935
Hanya awak.

36
00:02:43,246 --> 00:02:45,456
- Ya Tuhan.
- Max.

37
00:02:47,959 --> 00:02:51,004
Awak ada di sini.
Awak betul-betul ada di sini.

38
00:02:51,087 --> 00:02:52,589
Saya ada di sini.

39
00:02:53,298 --> 00:02:54,507
Selamat pulang, nak.

40
00:02:56,801 --> 00:02:58,052
Lambat betul, ya?

41
00:02:59,012 --> 00:03:00,388
Diamlah, Wheeler.

42
00:03:06,269 --> 00:03:07,353
Saya di mana?

43
00:03:08,771 --> 00:03:11,149
Ya, mesti awak keliru.

44
00:03:11,649 --> 00:03:13,735
Awak diburu oleh Demo-anjing.

45
00:03:13,818 --> 00:03:16,362
Sikit lagi kita semua nak kena makan

46
