48
00:03:21,367 --> 00:03:23,411
Gilalah! Mak!

49
00:03:25,246 --> 00:03:26,206
Vecna.

50
00:03:28,249 --> 00:03:29,542
Mesti dia marah.

51
00:03:30,585 --> 00:03:32,086
Dia akan cuba cari saya.

52
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:35,089
Dia tahu kami dapat keluar.

53
00:03:37,258 --> 00:03:38,218
Mana Holly?

54
00:03:41,012 --> 00:03:41,846
Mana dia?

55
00:05:59,442 --> 00:06:00,777
Jonathan.

56
00:06:02,195 --> 00:06:03,404
Jonathan.

57
00:06:03,488 --> 00:06:04,530
Jonathan.

58
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:06,783
Jonathan, sudahlah.

59
00:06:09,452 --> 00:06:10,536
Apa?

60
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:13,414
Kalau kita cedera, makin susah kita nanti.

61
00:06:14,665 --> 00:06:16,209
Ya, betul juga.

62
00:06:19,128 --> 00:06:20,380
Ya Tuhan.

63
00:06:23,174 --> 00:06:25,802
Okey, sekarang macam mana?

64
00:06:26,386 --> 00:06:27,887
Ada nak mengaku lagi?

65
00:06:36,729 --> 00:06:37,939
Ke belakang.

66
00:06:47,031 --> 00:06:48,408
Maaf sebab lambat.

67
00:06:53,246 --> 00:06:54,205
Awak okey tak?

68
00:06:54,288 --> 00:06:57,208
Ya. Ya, kami okey.

69
00:07:02,755 --> 00:07:03,756
Terima kasih.

70
00:07:05,675 --> 00:07:07,844
Pelikkah? Maaf. Memang pelik.

71
00:07:07,927 --> 00:07:08,761
Saya tak…

72
00:07:08,845 --> 00:07:10,430
Kami berdua ingat…

73
00:07:10,513 --> 00:07:12,682
- Kami dah mati. Ya, samalah.
- Ya.

74
00:07:12,765 --> 00:07:14,392
Penjana perisai kau itu…

75
00:07:14,475 --> 00:07:16,769
Bukan penjana perisai. Ya, kami tahu.

76
00:07:16,853 --> 00:07:20,022
Rasanya itu maklumat yang patut dikongsi.

77
00:07:20,106 --> 00:07:21,732
Ya, kami dah cuba.

78
00:07:21,816 --> 00:07:22,900
Antena patah.

79
00:07:22,984 --> 00:07:24,152
- Salah dia.
- Salah dia.

80
00:07:24,235 --> 00:07:26,904
Okey, jadi apa yang saya tembak?

81
00:07:26,988 --> 00:07:28,448
Jirim eksotik.

82
00:07:28,531 --> 00:07:30,867
Kau ingat kami tahu apa benda itu?

83
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:33,536
Semuanya ada di sini. Cuba tengok.

84
00:07:34,871 --> 00:07:37,206
Buku nota Dr. Brenner dari tahun 1983.

85
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:39,041
Ada banyak maklumat penting.

86
00:07:39,125 --> 00:07:43,379
Semua kajian dia tentang pintu itu,
cara dia cipta dan apa ia sebenarnya.

87
00:07:43,463 --> 00:07:45,214
Aku masih cuba tafsir, tapi…

88
00:07:45,298 --> 00:07:47,175
Meletup otak kalau nak faham.

89
00:07:47,258 --> 00:07:50,386
Kesimpulannya, Holly tak ada
di sebalik tembok itu.

90
00:07:53,222 --> 00:07:54,640
Jadi, dia di mana?

91
00:07:55,475 --> 00:07:57,602
Saya pun tak tahu,

92
00:07:57,685 --> 00:08:00,062
tapi bukan di Tempat Terbalik.

93
00:08:21,626 --> 00:08:25,004
Waktu dia culik saya,
dia buka pintu keempat dan terakhir.

94
00:08:25,087 --> 00:08:26,339
Hawkins terbelah dua.

95
00:09:05,253 --> 00:09:06,379
Kau boleh buat.

96
00:09:33,823 --> 00:09:35,700
- Apa itu?
- Apa?

97
00:09:36,951 --> 00:09:37,868
Holly.

98
00:10:39,513 --> 00:10:46,520
BABAK TUJUH: JAMBATAN

99
00:11:07,708 --> 00:11:08,668
Voyager Beta.

100
00:11:09,168 --> 00:11:10,086
Ada isyarat?

101
00:11:11,420 --> 00:11:14,090
Negatif, Voyager Alpha. Voyager Gamma?

102
00:11:14,674 --> 00:11:17,009
Kosong belaka di sini.

103
00:11:17,093 --> 00:11:19,637
Eksperimen belon awak tak berkesan, Manja.

104
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:22,556
Jom pasang antena pada van dan pandu saja.

105
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,975
Voyager Gamma, rupa bumi tak sekata

106
00:11:25,059 --> 00:11:26,727
dan banyak hutan di Hawkins,

107
00:11:26,811 --> 00:11:30,564
jadi kenderaan tak wajar digunakan
untuk kesan tag telemetri.

108
00:11:30,648 --> 00:11:34,276
"Wajar"? Dah enam jam
kita buat eksperimen belon awak.

109
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:37,029
Ya, tapi sebaik saja
kita menigasegi isyarat,

110
00:11:37,113 --> 00:11:39,699
saya dapat tentukan lokasi tepat Dustin.

111
00:11:39,782 --> 00:11:42,493
Apa pun tak boleh buat
kalau tak ada isyarat,

112
00:11:42,576 --> 00:11:45,496
jadi baik lepaskan saja
apa kita buat sekarang

113
00:11:45,579 --> 00:11:48,582
sebelum pelajar cemerlang awak
mati di dalam parit.

114
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:50,835
"Lepaskan…"

115
00:11:59,218 --> 00:12:01,095
Orang berani pasti bertuah.

116
00:12:04,432 --> 00:12:06,308
Saya dah dapat lokasi Dustin.

117
00:12:06,892 --> 00:12:08,269
Lepas belon, Voyager.

118
00:12:08,352 --> 00:12:10,020
- Boleh ulang?
- Kejap. Apa?

119
00:12:10,104 --> 00:12:14,066
Ia perlu naik lebih tinggi.
Lepaskan belon.

120
00:12:18,195 --> 00:12:19,572
Negatif 80!

121
00:12:20,197 --> 00:12:21,866
Negatif 44.

122
00:12:21,949 --> 00:12:25,161
Saya tarik balik, Manja.
Awak memang genius!

123
00:12:25,244 --> 00:12:28,164
Terima kasih.
Biar saya kira. Tunggu sekejap.

124
00:12:41,969 --> 00:12:46,265
Kau akan jadi pengintip aku

125
00:12:46,348 --> 00:12:50,019
buat kali terakhir.

126
00:12:55,483 --> 00:12:56,317
Will.

127
00:12:58,194 --> 00:13:00,154
Hopper baru hubungi mak di radio.

128
00:13:00,237 --> 00:13:02,406
Max selamat. Dia dah keluar.

129
00:13:04,325 --> 00:13:07,077
Hei, ini berita baik.

130
00:13:07,995 --> 00:13:10,831
Ini semua takkan berlaku
kalau bukan sebab kamu.

131
00:13:10,915 --> 00:13:12,124
Semuanya pasti okey.

132
00:13:12,792 --> 00:13:15,002
Tapi sampai bila, mak?

133
00:13:15,085 --> 00:13:17,880
Kalau betul cakap Lucas, hari ini harinya,

134
00:13:17,963 --> 00:13:19,757
hari Vecna akan bertindak.

135
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:22,718
Saya ingat saya mampu lawan dia,
tapi hakikatnya…

136
00:13:23,969 --> 00:13:26,806
Hakikatnya, saya tak ada peluang langsung.

137
00:13:28,015 --> 00:13:31,310
Dia tahu. Dia dah tahu sejak awal lagi.

138
00:13:31,811 --> 00:13:35,439
Dalam ramai-ramai orang di Hawkins,
ada sebab dia pilih saya.

139
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:40,110
Sebab dia tahu saya lemah,

140
00:13:40,194 --> 00:13:43,072
dan dia tahu dia boleh kawal saya.

141
00:13:43,155 --> 00:13:44,698
Tak betul.

142
00:13:44,782 --> 00:13:46,951
Betul, mak. Betul.

143
00:13:47,034 --> 00:13:48,744
Saya wadah dia.

144
00:13:49,745 --> 00:13:52,665
Wadah untuk menyalurkan kuasa dia,

145
00:13:52,748 --> 00:13:53,749
mengintip

146
00:13:54,333 --> 00:13:56,585
dan membina.

147
00:13:57,878 --> 00:14:00,214
"Membina"?

148
00:14:00,297 --> 00:14:01,924
Terowong-terowong itu.

149
00:14:02,883 --> 00:14:05,010
Ia tak terbentuk sendiri dari pintu.

150
00:14:05,594 --> 00:14:10,933
Setiap malam, saya terhubung dengan sarang
dan mengawal akar-akar menjalar

151
00:14:11,016 --> 00:14:12,852
untuk membentuk terowong

152
00:14:12,935 --> 00:14:16,188
dan menjangkiti dunia kita
dengan Tempat Terbalik.

153
00:14:16,981 --> 00:14:19,358
Begitu ramai orang mati disebabkan saya.

154
00:14:20,484 --> 00:14:22,695
Kalau saya mampu buat semua itu,

155
00:14:23,529 --> 00:14:27,032
apa agaknya dia mampu buat
dengan 12 lagi budak macam saya?

156
00:14:27,616 --> 00:14:29,159
Dengar sini.

157
00:14:29,243 --> 00:14:32,162
Segala benda yang terjadi
bukannya salah kamu.

158
00:14:32,246 --> 00:14:33,080
Faham tak?

159
00:14:33,664 --> 00:14:36,000
Pasal rancangan besar dia pula,

160
00:14:36,083 --> 00:14:38,961
dia takkan ada 12 wadah
atau apa-apalah namanya.

161
00:14:39,044 --> 00:14:42,339
Dia baru kehilangan Holly.
Holly tahu budak lain di mana.

162
00:14:42,423 --> 00:14:46,468
Sayang, ini belum berakhir.
Perjuangan kita masih panjang.

163
00:14:47,636 --> 00:14:48,679
Mak silap.

164
00:14:49,471 --> 00:14:50,890
Mak silap.

165
00:14:51,432 --> 00:14:52,975
Ini salah saya.

166
00:14:53,058 --> 00:14:53,934
Tidak.

167
00:14:54,602 --> 00:14:55,853
Tidak, sayang.

168
00:15:04,737 --> 00:15:06,280
Gerak!

169
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:20,169
Saya tak nampak di mana Holly akan sedar.

170
00:15:20,252 --> 00:15:22,880
Tapi saya agak,

171
00:15:23,923 --> 00:15:26,008
di mana-mana pun Vecna tahan dia,

172
00:15:26,842 --> 00:15:28,802
mesti di Tempat Terbalik.

173
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,221
Jadi,

174
00:15:32,222 --> 00:15:35,601
saya suruh dia balik ke rumah.

175
00:15:35,684 --> 00:15:37,645
Rumah? Maksudnya rumah kami?

176
00:15:37,728 --> 00:15:40,314
Kita kena masuk semula ke Tempat Terbalik.

177
00:15:40,397 --> 00:15:42,816
- Rekahan terdekat di mana?
- Cornwallis.

178
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:44,526
Lebih kurang 2.5 kilometer.

179
00:15:44,610 --> 00:15:45,986
Lucas, dengar tak?

180
00:15:46,070 --> 00:15:46,946
- Robin.
- Ya.

181
00:15:47,029 --> 00:15:47,863
Lucas!

182
00:15:50,282 --> 00:15:52,159
Aku tak boleh cakap sekarang.

183
00:15:52,242 --> 00:15:56,080
Vecna dah bunuh askar-askar itu,
jadi mudah nak masuk ke MAC.

184
00:15:56,163 --> 00:15:57,915
Tak. Mesti ada pasukan lain.

185
00:15:57,998 --> 00:15:59,541
Saya boleh pecahkan plat.

186
00:15:59,625 --> 00:16:04,213
Maksud kamu, Holly terperangkap
di bawah plat keluli?

187
00:16:04,296 --> 00:16:06,423
Bunyinya mungkin merisaukan,

188
00:16:06,507 --> 00:16:10,260
tapi dia bukannya dihempap
oleh kepingan keluli besar. Dia…

189
00:16:10,344 --> 00:16:11,512
Bagaimana nak kata?

190
00:16:11,595 --> 00:16:15,057
- Ada dunia di bawah dunia kita…
- Di bawah plat itu.

191
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,225
Tempat Terbalik.

192
00:16:16,308 --> 00:16:18,894
Ia macam Hawkins, tapi jauh lagi suram.

193
00:16:18,978 --> 00:16:20,562
Semua orang.

194
00:16:20,646 --> 00:16:22,356
Okey, mesti kamu tak percaya,

195
00:16:22,439 --> 00:16:26,026
tapi Erica dan En. Clarke
dah jumpa Dustin dan yang lain.

196
00:16:27,194 --> 00:16:30,781
Baiklah. Lagi senang
kalau mereka yang cari Holly.

197
00:16:33,409 --> 00:16:35,953
Baik kita cepat. Mereka datang.

198
00:16:47,923 --> 00:16:50,551
Hei, hei. Mak okey tak?

199
00:16:51,135 --> 00:16:52,428
Mak okey, Michael.

200
00:16:52,511 --> 00:16:54,304
Tak. Maaflah, puan tak okey.

201
00:16:54,388 --> 00:16:58,100
Puan boleh kena jangkitan,
perdarahan dan berhenti bernafas.

202
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:02,855
Kalau kamu fikir saya rela baring saja
sedangkan anak saya perlukan saya,

203
00:17:02,938 --> 00:17:06,025
kamu memang dah hilang akal. Mari pergi.

204
00:17:06,108 --> 00:17:08,652
Mak, mak. Betul cakap dia.

205
00:17:08,736 --> 00:17:10,279
Tak apa. Pergilah.

206
00:17:10,863 --> 00:17:12,990
Hei, mak dah selamatkan kami.

207
00:17:13,073 --> 00:17:14,533
Mak selamatkan kami.

208
00:17:14,616 --> 00:17:17,119
Ajaibnya, mak masih hidup, okey?

209
00:17:17,202 --> 00:17:20,414
Tapi percayalah cakap saya
yang kami mampu uruskannya.

210
00:17:20,497 --> 00:17:23,542
Mungkin banyak lagi makhluk itu di luar.

211
00:17:23,625 --> 00:17:25,335
Namanya Demogorgon. Saya tahu.

212
00:17:25,419 --> 00:17:29,798
Banyak benda saya perlu cerita
tentang Tempat Terbalik dan El,

213
00:17:29,882 --> 00:17:31,633
tapi mak cuma perlu tahu,

214
00:17:31,717 --> 00:17:34,887
kumpulan ini selamatkan Will
waktu tiada siapa mampu.

215
00:17:34,970 --> 00:17:36,180
Kami berjaya.

216
00:17:36,263 --> 00:17:38,390
Kami akan selamatkan Holly pula.

217
00:17:38,474 --> 00:17:42,436
Kami akan bawa dia balik.
Saya janji. Okey?

218
00:17:44,021 --> 00:17:44,855
Ya?

219
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:58,494
En. Clarke, terima kasih sebab tolong.

220
00:17:58,577 --> 00:17:59,661
Belum lagi.

221
00:17:59,745 --> 00:18:02,289
Kami menigasegi kedudukan Dustin ke sini,

222
00:18:02,372 --> 00:18:03,749
di tempat saya berdiri.

223
00:18:03,832 --> 00:18:06,043
Tapi waktu kami sampai, dia hilang.

224
00:18:06,126 --> 00:18:08,462
Dia bukan di sini. Dia di bawah sana.

225
00:18:09,463 --> 00:18:10,756
Apa?

226
00:18:11,507 --> 00:18:12,758
Kau tak beritahu dia?

227
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:14,760
- Aku…
- Beritahu apa?

228
00:18:14,843 --> 00:18:16,512
Biar betul!

229
00:18:17,554 --> 00:18:18,847
Biar betul.

230
00:18:19,598 --> 00:18:21,308
Hei, sini! Sini!

231
00:18:23,143 --> 00:18:24,603
Saya jumpa dia!

232
00:18:24,686 --> 00:18:26,480
Saya jumpa Dustin!

233
00:18:32,236 --> 00:18:33,946
- Saya tak dengar.
- Sabar.

234
00:18:35,322 --> 00:18:37,825
Ada sesiapa tak? Saya ulang, ini Dustin.

235
00:18:37,908 --> 00:18:39,201
Dustin, ini Mike.

236
00:18:39,284 --> 00:18:42,371
Holly lari daripada Vecna,
dan dia akan ke rumah aku.

237
00:18:42,454 --> 00:18:45,999
Pergi ke sana secepat mungkin
dan jumpa Holly. Dengar tak?

238
00:18:46,083 --> 00:18:49,461
Holly bukan di rumah.
Kami jumpa Holly. Aku ulang, kami…

239
00:18:49,545 --> 00:18:50,963
Dustin, tak jelas.

240
00:18:51,672 --> 00:18:52,673
Dustin?

